  <LI>
  <P style="MARGIN-TOP: 3px; MARGIN-BOTTOM: 3px">Neocles, Dedicated to Themista
  <LI>
  <P style="MARGIN-TOP: 3px; MARGIN-BOTTOM: 3px">Symposium
  <LI>
