  <LI>
  <P style="MARGIN-TOP: 3px; MARGIN-BOTTOM: 3px">Theories of the Passions, against Timocrates
  <LI>
  <P style="MARGIN-TOP: 3px; MARGIN-BOTTOM: 3px">Prognostication
  <LI>
  <P style="MARGIN-TOP: 3px; MARGIN-BOTTOM: 3px">Exhortation to Study Philosophy
  <LI>
  <P style="MARGIN-TOP: 3px; MARGIN-BOTTOM: 3px">On Images
