      <A href="#l18">To 
      Idomeneus</A></SPAN></B>
      <P 
      style="MARGIN-TOP: 8px; MARGIN-BOTTOM: 8px"><B><SPAN 
      style="FONT-SIZE: 10pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: Arial">19. 
      <A href="#l19">To 
      Craterus</A></SPAN></B>
      <P 
      style="MARGIN-TOP: 8px; MARGIN-BOTTOM: 8px"><B><SPAN 
