<BR><BR><P align=center><B><FONT face="arial, verdana"><A name=k43></A>43. 
Doctrine of the Elements (12 Books)</FONT></B>
<P align=center><FONT CLASS="ref"><B><A 
name=U56></A>[ U56 ]</FONT></B>
<P align=justify><B>Scholion on Epicurus<I>, Letter to Herodotus,</I> 
</B>by way of<B> Laertius, <I>Lives</I>, X.44: </B>He says below that 
