<P align=center><I><FONT face="arial, verdana">From Uncertain Volumes</FONT></I>
<P align=center><FONT CLASS="ref"><B><A 
name=U92></A>[ U92 ]</FONT></B>
<P align=left><B>Several Herculaneum Papyri comprise uncertain volumes 
from the series <I>On Nature.</I></B>
